###
# Replace <JWT_TOKEN> after login.
GET {{SmartHomeManager_HostAddress}}/api/Rooms
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <JWT_TOKEN>

###
GET {{SmartHomeManager_HostAddress}}/api/Devices
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <JWT_TOKEN>

###
GET {{SmartHomeManager_HostAddress}}/api/Automations
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <JWT_TOKEN>
